OL,3,CPrimary school closed as teachers
OL,4,Cstrike again over 'bullying'
OL,6,FTeachers at a primary school have gone
OL,7,Fon strike for a second time over
OL,8,Fallegations of bullying and
OL,9,Fintimidation.
OL,11,FSir Francis Primary School inwas
OL,12,Fclosed on Tuesday, 21 May, as staff
OL,13,Fmembers held a picket line outside the
OL,14,Fschool gates before moving to
OL,15,FtheCounty Council building.
OL,17,FThe National Education Union (NEU)
OL,18,Fsaid concerns raised by a
OL,19,Fwhistleblower last year have not been
OL,20,Fadequately resolved despite eight
OL,21,Fmembers of staff leaving.
