OL,4,Cstrike again over 'bullying'
OL,6,FNEU regional officer Kashmir Bilgan
OL,7,Fsaid: "There are issues around
OL,8,Fbullying, intimidation, and misogynist
OL,9,Fbehaviour which our members feel was
OL,10,Fcausing a very toxic environment.
OL,12,F"In the end our members had enough.
OL,13,FEnough was enough. They wanted the
OL,14,Fgoverning body to take some action and
OL,15,Fsort it out so that it would become a
OL,16,Fdecent working place."
OL,18,FShe added: "It's management practices
OL,19,Fand we want the governing body to
OL,20,Freact to that and sort that out.
