OL,6,F"At the end of the day, our members
OL,7,Fjust want to do what they're there to
OL,8,Fdo which is educate young people"
OL,10,F, which saw the school either closed
OL,11,For partly closed.
OL,13,FDavid Reed, chair of governors at Sir
OL,14,FFrancis Hill said: "We are involved in
OL,15,Fongoing discussion to find a solution
OL,16,Fin the best interests of all involved.
OL,18,F"We have taken part in constructive
OL,19,Fmeetings with both the Trades Unions
OL,20,Fand ACAS and hope to reach a
OL,21,Fresolution in the very near future.
